{"name":"Possessed Pelican","size":"medium","type":"Monstrosity","tag":"","alignment":"chaotic evil","hitDice":"9","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"11","speed":"20","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"40","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"38 (7d8 + 7)","speedDesc":"20 ft., fly 40 ft.","strPoints":"12","dexPoints":"13","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"7","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"13","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The harpy can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The harpy regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the harpy can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the harpy can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The harpy can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the harpy's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the harpy's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the harpy dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Flyby","desc":"The [MON] doesn't provoke opportunity attacks when it flies out of an enemy's reach."}],"actions":[{"name":"Rancid Breath (1d4)","desc":"The [MON] exhales rancid air in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking [1D12] poison damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one."},{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two attacks: one with its claws and one with its beak."},{"name":"Claws","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 6 (2d4 + 1) slashing damage."},{"name":"Beak","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D12] bludgeoning damage."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Bitter Blood","desc":"If the [MON] is below it's hp minimum and is grappled or hit with an unarmed attack, it spews it's gross blood all over everything, the attacking creature takes [2d4] poison damage."},{"name":"Carry-Out","desc":"If the [MON] reduces a creature to 0hp it grabs its head in it's beak and can fly it's speed."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}